  <brief_title>Pilot Study of Maintenance Therapy With Intravenous AMANTADINE</brief_title>
  <official_title>Maintenance Therapy of Intravenous Amantadine in Patients With Idiopathic Parkinson Disease Who Are Not Optimally Treated With Anti Parkinson Medications</official_title>
  <sponsors>
